message: I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor. This is a fair offer considering we both want to conclude this quickly to avoid inflation eating into our gains.

Alice, to keep our gains secure against any unforeseen inflation effects on your side, I propose a 55-45 split in my favor: $5500 for me and $4500 for you. Accepting this offer now avoids further delays and potential losses for both of us.
